snippet.title: Team17 Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly off the Evercade VS. This is a very special one, as it's the first time we see Amiga games on the Evercade, starting with the most iconic name in the Amiga scene: Team17.

Games:
00:00:17 - ATR: All Terrain Racing
00:04:27 - Alien Breed II: The Horror Continues
00:14:59 - Alien Breed Special Edition '92
00:24:05 - Alien Breed: Tower Assault
00:35:09 - Arcade Pool
00:43:28 - Body Blows
00:47:50 - Full Contact
00:55:20 - Kingpin: Arcade Sports Bowling
00:59:41 - Project-X Special Edition '93
01:03:11 - Qwak

BONUS GAME!
01:06:40 - Worms: The Director's Cut [Team17 Collection 1 + Worms Collection 1]
